@startuml state-coppa-consent
title COPPA Consent State Machine

[*] --> PendingConsent : Parent account created

PendingConsent : Consent not yet provided
PendingConsent : Child profiles locked
PendingConsent --> ConsentSubmitted : Parent selects\nverification method

ConsentSubmitted : Awaiting verification
ConsentSubmitted --> ConsentVerified : Verification\nsuccessful
ConsentSubmitted --> PendingConsent : Verification\nfailed / expired

ConsentVerified : Child profiles unlocked
ConsentVerified : Consent record stored
ConsentVerified --> ConsentRevoked : Parent revokes\nconsent

ConsentRevoked : Child profiles deactivated
ConsentRevoked : Data deletion scheduled
ConsentRevoked --> PendingConsent : Parent re-initiates\nconsent

@enduml
